Responsibilities
WORK FOR US. Strategic Review is looking for a highly motivated person to manage office operations and relationships with Suppliers, Distributors and Subscribers.  Knowledge of Accounting is a plus. Requirement : Have a minimum of a Bachelor’s degree in Administration, Accounting, Management or other relevant subjects, or have equivalent professional experienceHave a minimum of 5 years-experience in a similar role; experience in publishing is definitely a plusBe able to show initiative and autonomy in conducting tasks & responsibilities, especially in maintaining publication workflow, meeting deadlines and general project managementBe able to build and maintain relationships with suppliers, distributors and subscribersBe fluent in English and Bahasa Indonesia (spoken and written)Be familiar with basic accounting and bookkeepingBe experienced in working at a senior management levelBe experienced with Microsoft OfficeA basic knowledge of graphic design software will be a plus  To apply: Please submit your application with the subject heading “General Affairs”, current CV and supporting documents (no larger than 2MB) before May 11, 2014 to:atria.rai@sr-indonesia.comPosition is available now
